{"id": 7072, "source": "pestle", "subject": "chemistry", "course": null, "level": "SL", "paper": "1", "year": "2017", "session": "17M", "subtopic": "9-1-oxidation-and-reduction", "title": "17M.1.SL.TZ1.22", "topic_id": "9", "source_url": "https://pestle.pages.dev/app/", "question_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p>What is the oxidation half-equation in the redox reaction?</p>\n<p>2S<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub><sup>2–</sup>(aq) + I<sub>2</sub>(aq) → S<sub>4</sub>O<sub>6</sub><sup>2–</sup>(aq) + 2I<sup>–</sup>(aq)</p>\n<p>A.     I<sub>2</sub>(aq) + 2e<sup>–</sup> → 2I<sup>–</sup>(aq)</p>\n<p>B.     2I<sup>–</sup>(aq) → I<sub>2</sub>(aq) + 2e<sup>–</sup></p>\n<p>C.     2S<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub><sup>2–</sup>(aq) → S<sub>4</sub>O<sub>6</sub><sup>2–</sup>(aq) + 2e<sup>–</sup></p>\n<p>D.     S<sub>4</sub>O<sub>6</sub><sup>2–</sup>(aq) + 2e<sup>–</sup> → 2S<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub><sup>2–</sup>(aq)</p>\n</div>", "solution_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p>C</p>\n</div>", "examiners_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n[N/A]\n</div>"}